    <p>This vol­un­tary wel­fare or­gan­i­sa­tion is al­ways on the look­out for vol­un­teers and do­na­tions. Find out more at www.be­yond.org.sg/vol­un­teer.</p>
    <p>NEW LIFE STO­RIES</p>
    <p>This non-profit or­gan­i­sa­tion is hop­ing to raise $15,000 for its Close The Gap campaign, which will pro­vide chil­dren with a cre­ative ac­tiv­ity pack in­spired by the book Near And Far. Do­nate at www.giv­ing.sg/new-life-sto­ries/clos­ethe­gap.</p>
    <p>TAK TAKUT KIDS CLUB</p>
    <p>Run by com­mu­nity arts group 3Pump­kins, this kids’ club needs at least $1,900 a month to cover rental costs. Learn more at www.3pump­kins.co/sup­port.</p>


